snippet.title: Pie in the Sky - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as the feared, Australian Magpie in this old-school, action, arcade game!

Swoop people, steal food, poop on your foes and generally cause chaos in iconic Australian locations!

Coming to Steam in early 2025: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2941360/Pie_in_the_Sky/
Coming to consoles and mobile late 2025.
Join the discord now! https://discord.gg/QvfZYqH5v8
Support the development: https://ko-fi.com/monstershopgames

https://monstershopgames.com/

Music Credit - "Bird Attack" by Frenzal Rhomb
